<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉，<delay8 />
你現在不要接近我比較好！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不想把這股怒火發洩在你身上<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這難以平息的憤怒<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我該如何是好啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無法抑制的焦躁<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會試著正面應對，<delay20 />
這名為「憤怒」的負面情緒！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay8 />這個人啊，<delay20 />
就是神經太大條啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得，<delay20 />
最近的占卜<delay8 />容易讓人感到迷惘～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然從以前到現在，<delay20 />
我曾被比喻成各式各樣的東西，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但這次也太超過了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的星座占卜說，<delay20 />
我的幸運物<delay8 />是<tag a="135" b="5" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我不知道該怎麼辦，<delay20 />
於是找<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />商量<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<gender3 m="他" f="她" />竟然說，<delay20 />
「我從以前就覺得<delay20 />你很像<tag a="135" b="5" arg="0xcd00" />。」<delay frames="40" />
這種失禮的話！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />別把那些話放在心上</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />是喔</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對吧！<delay frames="40" />
聽到<tag a="110" b="4" />這麼說，<delay8 />
我舒坦多了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過最近有很多
充滿暗示性的幸運物，<delay20 />
真是讓人困擾啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我很氣占卜的內容，<delay20 />
但<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />……<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />也很過分！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
沒想到<delay8 />
你竟然是這種人！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說<tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們先暫時跟彼此保持距離吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別看我這樣，<delay20 />
我真的很生氣<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
我也是會生氣的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對不起</message>
	<message label="203_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我明白了……</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />OK！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看起來已經有好好反省，<delay20 />
那我就不計較了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="30" />唉<tag a="110" b="0" />算了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生氣果然是件累人的事，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你下次可別犯同樣的錯喔。</message>
</msbt>